{"tid":2179464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京親口證實「俄國特遣警備團」已為白俄羅斯待命","createTime":"2020-08-29T06:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T07:10:33.000Z","uid":34410,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"75bc1d6f269280deabed9bbe987e332e3c9164e8","tid":2179464,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"「只要街頭出現『暴徒』，俄國警隊就會出手、接管鎮壓！」俄國總統普丁27日晚間藉由官媒專訪，首度就白俄羅斯的全國反獨裁示威「親口表態」。發言中，普丁雖強調俄國目前仍在觀望、並肯定「歐洲最後獨裁者」盧卡申科（Alexander Lukashenko）的「維穩效率」；但普丁同時也證實「我早已應盧卡申科的拜托，召集了一支『後備警備隊』...俄國隨時都能開進白俄羅斯」&mdash;&mdash;普丁的發言，是白俄羅斯大選舞弊衝突3個星期以來，莫斯科最為具體的「恫嚇表態」。而俄方態度的轉硬，不僅顯示白俄羅斯的公民抗爭，正已快速步入「全國總鎮壓」的攤牌時刻；另一方面，則更可能與普丁政敵納瓦爾尼（Alexei Navalny）遭投毒命危案而連動震盪的「歐俄戰略槓桿」有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://global.udn.com/global_vision/amp/story/8662/4816401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Famp%2Fstory%2F8662%2F4816401&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=fd3f3545\" target=\"_blank\">https://global.udn.com/global_vision/amp/story/8662/4816401</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fB2uJwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfB2uJwu.jpg&h=72fda40c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快有俄羅斯人民志願軍準備開入明斯克<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92590e9c20703975f6ecee72abe17e7bcead20d3","tid":2179464,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"普京幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f94f2f2c34d4673b6a862e0fb93d5f73a6dec6d","tid":2179464,"uid":330227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/